  "title": "A delta shaped UFO was sighted above the airport in Belém-PA [1994]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/01/a-delta-shaped-ufo-was-sighted-above-the-airport-in-belem-pa-1994/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1jO",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>NOV 26th, 1994</strong>. Time: 00:40 am. Duration: less than one minute. Six people observed an unidentified flying object near the landing strip at Belém Airport, in the State of Pará. According to witnesses, the UFO was &#8220;delta&#8221; shaped, small and its colors &#8220;varied between green and orange&#8221;. Still according to the report, the speed of the unknown object was &#8220;superior to the speed of a Boeing 737&#8221; and the UFO was seen flying from East to West. The sighting was done with the naked eye and with good visibility, not being filmed or photographed.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.383. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Belém, Estado do Pará”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
